Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心理作用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我安份点\N马上就会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第141话 被释放的妖马炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才不是才吃过鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又没有吃到饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话\N就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着什么吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N我是没有带什么啦  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有饭吃了\N吃饭  吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  神官大人被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是指最近频传的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门杀害那些\N道行高深的神官和僧人这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道\N到底是什么人干的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一直发展到现在\N事情绝不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为这样\N被封印在神社里的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每到晚上就出来作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以村子才这么荒凉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有气味\N虽然只是杂碎妖怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我\N我一招就把他们通通解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样的事情\N在这附近经常发生是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  到处都是这样的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛抢我的  还我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高僧和神官\N接二连三地遭到杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底会是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手好像是一个\N抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么听来\N那个女人想必是神乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个时候\N还以人类为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情怎么样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正如果这件事跟\N奈落那个家伙扯上关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不能袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  现在神乐在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个倒不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近最有名气的僧人\N或神官是哪一位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是问还在世的高僧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近还活着的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来最有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是万愿寺的神泉和尚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉和尚?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指那位神泉和尚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听过他的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N是一位很有名的僧人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说论起封印妖怪的功力\N无人能出其右啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连身为驱魔师的我也听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是非常有名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是封印了那个\N人称炼狱鬼的食人妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他骑的妖马“炎蹄”\N这个传说是最为有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问您怎么了吗  神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…可能是我多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像感觉到炎蹄在嘶鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是封印在\N我们后山祠堂的妖马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄正如其名\N是一匹有着火焰马蹄的马妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是传说中能够日行千里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚力非凡的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据传说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相隔百年前有一匹神马\N被卷入大火之中死去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的怨灵出现在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且随着火山爆发\N转生成为炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  都还不清楚咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过传说还不只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于炎蹄还有另外一个传说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑上炎蹄的话\N就能够取得天下?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么人传开的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这种说法广为流传
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然这种说法\N只不过是一种迷信罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为了炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类跟妖怪之间的争斗\N却没有停止过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了跟人类与妖怪\N无数次的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后生存下来的炼狱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄给予他骑上它的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得到了炎蹄的炼狱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得气势逼人狂暴无比
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为炼狱鬼的四处作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而让村民们感到痛苦不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是拜托了神泉和尚\N为他们驱魔除妖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我跟炼狱鬼的战斗\N持续了三天三夜的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为了要封印炎蹄\N耗个三天三夜也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易\N打败了这两个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且分别封印在\N两个不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个祠堂也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说起来\N已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉和尚能够打败\N如此厉害妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一位非常了不起的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过既然是能够\N封印那种妖怪的和尚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐会盯上他\N也没什么好奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N既然如此我们快点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间在这里磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爱使唤别人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么地方不对劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都没有感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座寺庙的附近\N有邪气正在逼近当中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快点去躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟之前的那些家伙比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像稍微厉害了一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身吧  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为是的布下结界了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说杀害高僧的妖怪\N是个抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你们杀害了\N那些僧人跟神官的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这个婴儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个女人\N恐怕还要凶恶好几倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我窥视到\N此世与彼世的交界处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和尚  下一招你还避得开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这一招又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙蛇之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好地来窥视你的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成…功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…毕竟也老了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子…恐怕不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上有香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事的地点恐怕是寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神乐下的手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还留有那家伙的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下手的\N是一个抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父很勇敢地\N跟那个妖怪战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜为了保护\N我们两个人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易\N把两个妖怪其中一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个婴儿成功地消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父的法力将他劈成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个婴儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落在白灵山之中\N再次诞生出来的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在白灵山魔塌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还特地带那个婴儿逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落来说\N他应该是相当重要的存在对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  总觉得没这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最猛胜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想带我去什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神无
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落派你来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成\N你是代替奈落来教训我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个由神乐来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正迟早有一天\N会变成这个样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窥视此世与彼世的交界处?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在杀了师父之前\N那个婴儿就是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么窥视心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐和婴儿\N到处杀害神官和高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来觉得是为了\N把被封印住的妖怪们给解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来似乎没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此世与彼世的交界处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是那个妖怪的封印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么封印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后山是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们师父\N好不容易用他的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印住的一匹\N叫做炎蹄的妖马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个叫炼狱鬼\N所骑的那匹妖马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  你们也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是犬夜叉  那匹妖马…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好跟它算个帐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这里来了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  既然如此我就用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  那匹马冲来冲去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别管我\N一定要想办法阻止那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本就瞄不准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点阻止\N那匹妖马的行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它停止移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来你就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候干嘛阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  大家快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它一定是想要去找\N被封印的主人炼狱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快点追吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下一半\N是要我怎么处理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点气息都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你复活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活过来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:22:00.77,ED,,0,0,0,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:16.82,ED,,0,0,0,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:22.89,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:26.42,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:32.62,ED,,0,0,0,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:50.84,ED,,0,0,0,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:53.94,ED,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you I'll be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:58.62,ED,,0,0,0,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:05.02,ED,,0,0,0,,So Come my way
